## How the App Is Deployed

- **Web:** Vercel at https://dopamind-w3fp.vercel.app
- **Mobile:** Capacitor wraps this Vercel URL — Android/iOS WebView points at production Vercel. No local bundled web build for the live app shell.
- **Android:** `android/` in repo, open in Android Studio.
- **iOS:** Not yet generated (`npx cap add ios` not run yet).

### Capacitor Config (`capacitor.config.ts`)

- `appId`: `com.dopamind.app`
- `appName`: `Dopamind`
- `webDir`: `out`
- `server.url`: `https://dopamind-w3fp.vercel.app` — loads from Vercel, not local

### Key Capacitor Commands

```bash
npx cap sync android      # after any config/web change
npx cap sync ios          # after any config/web change
npx cap open android      # opens Android Studio
npx cap add ios           # generates iOS project (NOT DONE YET)
```

**Rule:** After ANY change to `capacitor.config.ts`, run `npx cap sync android` (and `ios` when applicable), then rebuild in Android Studio / Xcode.

