## Database Tables (Supabase)

- `users` — id, plan (`'free'`|`'pro'`), `trial_ends_at`, `created_at`, `consent_version` (survey JSON)
- `tasks` — id, user_id, title, bucket, status, priority, steps (jsonb), created_at, completed_at
- `forest_trees` — id, user_id, task_id, tree_type, status, timer_duration, grown_at, died_at
- `user_streaks` — id, user_id, current_streak, longest_streak, last_active_date, total_trees_grown, total_trees_lost, forest_acres
- `leaderboard` — id, user_id, display_name, current_streak, forest_size, total_trees, rank
- `daily_reflections` — id, user_id, energy_level, mood_level, notes, plan_date
- `focus_sessions` — id, user_id, task_id, duration_s, completed
- `medication_reminders` — id, user_id, reminder_time, label, active

---

## Timer → Tree Type

| Minutes | Tree |
|---------|------|
| 5 | sprout |
| 15 | baby |
| 25 | half |
| 30 | flowering |
| 45 | large (tall pine) |
| 60 | full (grand lush) |
| abandoned | dead (grey bare trunk) |

