## Design System

- Primary green: `#16A34A` — buttons, active states
- Dark green: `#15803D` — gradient end, hover
- Purple: `#7C3AED` — PRO badges, AI features
- Blue: `#2563EB` — AI planner accent
- Background: `#FFFFFF` — Card: `#F8FAFC`, border: `#F1F5F9`
- Text: `#1E293B` — secondary: `#64748B` — muted: `#94A3B8`
- Danger: `#EF4444` — Warning: `#F59E0B`

Cards: `rounded-2xl p-4`. Buttons: `rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold` — green gradient. PRO badge: ~8px text, gradient `#7C3AED` → `#2563EB`. Layout: `max-w-2xl mx-auto` where appropriate.

