## Hard Rules for Cursor

- Every React component file: `'use client'` at top
- Auth: always `supabase.auth.getUser()` — never hardcode user IDs
- Timer state: always `useTimer()` from `@/context/timer-context` — never local-only timer state for app-wide behavior
- Supabase in components: `@/lib/supabase/client` | in API routes / server: `@/lib/supabase/server`
- AI prompts stay in API routes only — not in frontend string prompts for model calls
- Animations: Framer Motion — only animate `transform` and `opacity`
- Never `transition-all` — specify the property
- Never use default Tailwind blue/indigo as primary brand color
- Never duplicate components or API routes without checking existing ones
- Never commit `.env.local`
- Capacitor: after **any** `capacitor.config.ts` change → `npx cap sync android` (and iOS when project exists) → rebuild native app

### Environment variable names (never paste values in chat)

`NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`, `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`, `GROQ_API_KEY`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_ENV`

